# Cursor Entry

For `run issue ...`, do not use duplicated local stage scripts.

Use:
- `.ai/WORKFLOW.md` as orchestration source
- `.ai/PIPELINE.md` for stage details
- `.ai/agents/` for stage behaviors

Workflow stages:
1. Issue Intake (+ optional Figma)
2. Planning
3. Implementation (Logic + UI)
4. Build (no tests, max 10 min)
5. Code Review
6. Design Review (if Figma)
7. Test Authoring
8. Test Run
9. Branch + Commit + PR

Required logs per stage:
- `Start stage <n>: <name>`
- `Stage <n>: <name> completed`

Artifacts:
- `.ai/artifacts/run/MS-<run-id>-<stage>-<name>.md`
